product_name: Benchmark Maps Washington Recreation Map - Folded
long_description: Plan your next adventure in Washington with this handy recreation map! Offers information on boating, fishing, skiing and camping. Map features color-coded land ownership graph and other demographic information. Map unfolds to 38.5 x 26.5 inches. Scale 1:650,000. Benchmark Maps; copyright 2005.
